    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's an interesting way to frame it. So, if I'm teaching this to my class, should I tell them that the critics who claim it's just \"judicial activism\" are basically just trying to limit the protection of civil rights, or is there actually any weight to their legal argument that we should present as a legitimate perspective?",
